OL,3,C300% rise in antisemitism in Wales is
OL,4,C'unprecedented since the Holocaust'
OL,6,FThere were three times more
OL,7,Fantisemitic incidents reported across
OL,8,FWales last year compared with 2022,
OL,9,Faccording to the latest data from a
OL,10,FJewish charity.
OL,12,FThe Community Support Trust (CST) said
OL,13,F57 incidents were reported, ranging
OL,14,Ffrom threats and abusive behaviour to
OL,15,Fassault. That compares to just 13
OL,16,Ftotal reports in 2022, representing a
OL,17,Frise of 338%.
OL,19,FIt was announced by the prime minister
OL,20,Fon Thursday that for security, through
OL,21,Ffunding for the charity, CST.
