OL,6,FSheila Gewolb, who represents the
OL,7,FCardiff United Synagogue on the Board
OL,8,Fof Deputies of British Jews, said the
OL,9,Fexperience of Jewish people living in
OL,10,FWales since the October 7th attacks in
OL,11,FIsrael have been "unprecedented since
OL,12,Fthe Holocaust".
OL,14,F"There was just shock that this could
OL,15,Fhappen in this day and age", Sheila
OL,16,Ftold ITV Wales, regarding the Hamas
OL,17,Fterror attack.
