OL,6,F"Initially we had the sympathy of the
OL,7,Fworld that this terrible thing had
OL,8,Fhappened... that 1,200 young people
OL,9,Fhad been murdered at a music festival,
OL,10,Fthat 300 hostages had been taken.
OL,12,F"That lasted for about five days and
OL,13,Fthen Israel decided to defend itself
OL,14,Fand then we lost the public support,
OL,15,Fwhen people saw the awful things
OL,16,Fhappening to the poor Palestinians".
OL,18,FThe president of the Jewish Society at
OL,19,F, Jess Steinberg, told ITV Wales that
OL,20,Fshe has witnessed more antisemitism
OL,21,Fsince the war broke out.
